guage:** Python  \n**Size:** M\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Overview of MetadataService and data models]\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: [TO BE FILLED]\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Describe scenarios]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775876548051,"end":1775876548074}}}}
