0% |\n65: \n66: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/0 tasks)**\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## References\n71: \n72: - cli-toolkit/design.md — CLI toolkit architecture\n73: - cli-toolkit/spec.md — CLI specification\n\n(End of file - total 73 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage pending] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: [TO BE FILLED]\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: [TO BE FILLED]\n  - Purpose: [TO BE FILLED]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775876565227,"end":1775876565245}}}}
